title: Did Greta Thunberg Disguise Herself as Pro-Trump Rioter?
subtitle: If so, an uncredited meme would not likely be the first to report the discovery.
author: Jessica Lee
vclaim: A meme showed environmental activist Greta Thunberg in disguise as a member of the pro-Trump crowd that stormed the U.S. Capitol on Jan. 6, 2021.
